{"tid":1476640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"為老人量身訂做！日研發「機械尾巴」　助老人平衡避免摔倒","createTime":"2019-08-16T01:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T01:50:02.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5aadee67fe588b7d6e714dc4c652c5dd1051e5","tid":1476640,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:17:44.000Z","msg":"日本社會嚴重高齡化，科學家針對老人研發新科技，像是日本慶應義塾大學研究團隊，設計出一款人類專用的機械尾巴，外型如同海馬尾巴、如同鐘擺一樣，當人體往一個方向傾斜、尾巴往相反方向移動，可幫助老人保持平衡、避免跌倒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXx728p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXx728p.jpg&h=6232a0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身體往下或是左右側彎，背後這個長得像尾巴的裝置就會跟著變換角度，這是由日本慶應義塾大學研究團隊設計出的人類專用「機械尾巴」。<br />\n<br />\n尾巴的整體結構是從海馬尾巴得到靈感，設計來處理大量力量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qq8SuOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqq8SuOy.jpg&h=1491b084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機械尾巴使用4塊人工肌肉，依據驅動肌肉進行8個方向的移動。日本社會嚴重高齡化，機械尾巴目前仍處於實驗階段，未來可望幫助老人活動避免跌倒受傷。<br />\n<br />\n當你踩階梯開高處櫃子或是搬重物上樓梯時，都容易失去重心跌倒，這款機械尾巴長約1公尺，如同鐘擺一樣，當人體往一個方向傾斜、尾巴往相反方向移動，幫助配戴者保持平衡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WY87iHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWY87iHa.jpg&h=deead8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新科技幫助人類生活更便利，美國社交平台Snapchat母公司Snap，發表第三代Spectacles太陽眼鏡，可用來拍攝3D立體照片，上傳到Snapchat平台分享，一副定價380美元約11000台幣，儘管比第一代貴上2倍，已經吸引許多網美搶著訂購，走在潮流尖端。"},{"pid":"0968f4a591cc5a3386ae085d0bc015c54ba46e5c","tid":1476640,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅大好機會！！十八區we connect，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823人鏈823人鏈823人鏈</span></span></strong>，百萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"22f70460d364bd5e5210cf888343abfa669f186f","tid":1476640,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0WQd7h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0WQd7h.gif&h=2f8b1f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99e0998dcc390f4a2a28d2a0347fb7e503793374","tid":1476640,"uid":223486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個發明唔錯"},{"pid":"6b5d2aa805801c0898f2b0ded4956b20a80c809d","tid":1476640,"uid":41216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:37:52.000Z","msg":"俾經常仆街既警狗？"},{"pid":"564f32c8f287809a9be542c1a5e12d2af478014e","tid":1476640,"uid":11067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVRAsHv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVRAsHv.png&h=bdd174ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60787cbe6ef6355221c88875a3def0a0fdb0230f","tid":1476640,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:40:53.000Z","msg":"香港創科：八段錦app"},{"pid":"246f8a882e720e9d6fd652203c959f99140a13bd","tid":1476640,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa7bb5897d04e355786f342f289ddc8bea41ad9","tid":1476640,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"向後跌咁點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"